{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_05_02",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 2話 似た者同士達",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃！？　どうしたんだ、そんなに慌てて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono!? What's wrong? Why are you so flustered?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "私、私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんの説得に失敗しました～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I failed to persuade Rio-san~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "だから言ったろ……まったく。そうやって一度決めたら\n真っ直ぐ突っ込んでいくところは麻奈そっくりだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See‚ I told you… Geez. Just like I said‚ once you've made up your mind‚\nyou charge straight ahead. That's so much like Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんとそっくり、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You think I'm just like big sis?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃も見たことあるだろう？\n麻奈がなんにでも真っ直ぐなところは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've seen it too‚ right‚ Kotono?\nMana always goes straight for everything.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば……私が小学生の時、帰り道で\n男子グループにからかわれたことがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it… When I was in elementary school‚\non my way home‚ I was being teased by a group of boys.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "どうしようかと思ってたら、そこに偶然お姉ちゃんが\n現れて男子達を叱ったんです。何してるの！　って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't know what to do‚ but then‚ by chance‚ big sis showed up\nand scolded the boys. She said‚ \"What are you doing!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "その時は凄く安心したんですけど……男子の一人の\nお兄さん……高校生くらいの人が出てきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I felt so relieved at that moment… but then‚ one of the boys‚\nan older guy‚ maybe high school age‚ came forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……大丈夫だったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Was everything okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "それが……お姉ちゃんてば、一歩も引かないどころか\nその高校生にまでお説教を始めたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… big sis‚ instead of backing down even a step‚\nstarted lecturing the high schooler.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "「か弱い女子二人に向かって拳を振り上げるなんて\n恥ずかしくないのか。出直して来なさい」……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said‚ \"Are you not ashamed\nof raising your fist against two fragile girls? Get lost!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "なんとも麻奈らしいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's so typical of Mana…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "結局お姉ちゃんが全員追い払っちゃいました\nでも……私は、その後の方がよく覚えてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ big sis drove them all away.\nBut… I remember what happened afterward quite well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "二人きりになった途端にお姉ちゃんが抱きしめて\nくれたんですけど……お姉ちゃん、震えてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As soon as we were alone‚ big sis hugged me tightly‚\nand she was trembling…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、お姉ちゃんはこんなに怖かったのに\nそれを少しも表に出さずに私を守ってくれたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ even though big sis was so scared‚\nshe held me and protected me without showing any of it on the outside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "そんな風に思ったら……次の日から、男子に\nからかわれても全然気にならなくなりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I thought about it that way…\nI stopped caring about being teased by boys the next day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈から勇気を学んだんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You learned courage from Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "そう……かもしれません。まぁ、今回の件は\n勇気とは違うのかもしれませんけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… maybe. Well‚ this time‚\nit might not be courage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……莉央さんは、麻奈のことを大切に思うからこそ\n自分から線を引いてると思うんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I think Rio-san is keeping her distance because she cares about Mana.\nIt's like she's drawing the line herself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "それ……葵さんも同じこと言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi-san said the same thing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shibuya-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shibuya-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、やっぱり、{user}さんは\nみんなのことをよく見てるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ as expected‚ {user}-san‚\nyou're really observant when it comes to everyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャーなんだから、これくらい当たり前だよ\nもう事務所に着くから、続きはその後だな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I am the manager‚ so it's only natural.\nWe're almost at the office‚ so we'll continue later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 150.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの話なんですけど……莉央さんに断られた後\n葵さんに呼び止められたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About what I was talking about earlier… After getting rejected by Rio-san‚\nI was stopped by Aoi-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "それで、アルバムの前に、まず私がリズノワのライブに\nゲスト出演したらどうかな……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ she suggested that before the album‚ I should first make a guest appearance\nat a LizNoir live performance… How about that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "葵がそんな提案を琴乃に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aoi made that suggestion to you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "私達だけじゃなくて\nリズノワも変化している途中なのかもしれないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just us‚\nLizNoir might also be in the middle of changing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのかもな。しかし……葵の提案であっても\n莉央さんは反対するかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That could be the case. However… even if it's Aoi's suggestion‚\nRio-san might oppose it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "むむ……頑固ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm… She's so stubborn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それは琴乃もだろ？　今回はやけに押しが強いし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren't you stubborn too? You're unusually persistent this time‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃に莉央さんに、麻奈……\n三人とも案外似てるのかもな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "with Rio-san‚ with Kotono… and with Mana…\nThe three of you might actually have more in common than you think.",
