      },
      "startTime": 210.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "「何がなんでも私の仕事を減らそうとするんだから！」\nってぷりぷりしてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"You're always trying to reduce my workload no matter what!\"\nShe was pouting as she said that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "えっ。いや、あの頃は麻奈が全然休もうとしないから\nこっちも意地になって……なんで笑ってるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Well‚ back then‚ Mana never wanted to take a break‚ so\nI became stubborn too‚ out of pride… Why are you laughing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn025.m4a",
      "text": "頑固者って言うといつも反撃される、って\n言ってましたよ。口が減らないんだからって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She told me that whenever someone calls you stubborn‚\nyou always retaliate and never back down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "俺の行動を読み過ぎだろ、麻奈のやつ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana reads my actions too well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
