      },
      "startTime": 240.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな、似た者同士なんだと思う\n琴乃も、莉央さんも、麻奈も、俺も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ that's right. I think we're quite alike.\nKotono‚ Rio-san‚ Mana‚ and me.",
