      },
      "startTime": 250,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn027.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんのこと……なんとかならないでしょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is there no way to resolve things with Rio-san?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "今は琴乃と莉央さんの意見はぶつかってるけど\nお互いの麻奈を大切に思う気持ちは同じなはずだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ your opinions clash‚ but\nthe feelings of cherishing Mana are the same for both of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "二人でゆっくり話し合ってみたらどうだ？\nそうすればきっと、納得出来る答えが見つかると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if you two sit down and have a calm discussion?\nI believe that way you'll find an answer that satisfies both sides.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 268.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_05_02-ktn028.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですね。まだ私、莉央さんの気持ちを\nちゃんと聞いてませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… You're right.\nI haven't really listened to Rio-san's feelings yet.",
